      "parameters": {
        "width": 704,
        "height": 1360,
        "content": "Turn a simple email workflow into a **LinkedIn content machine**. Generate post ideas, draft full posts, and auto-publish to LinkedIn ‚Äî all controlled by replying to emails.  \n\n---\n\n## üìå Purpose  \nAutomate your LinkedIn posting pipeline using **AI + Email approvals**.  \n- Generate **10 scroll-stopping post ideas** tailored to your niche & audience.  \n- Approve your favorite by replying to the email with a number.  \n- Receive **3 AI-written drafts** for the chosen idea.  \n- Pick your favorite draft via email reply.  \n- The selected post gets **auto-published to LinkedIn** ‚úÖ.  \n- All steps are logged in **Google Sheets**.  \n\n---\n\n## üîó Apps Used  \n- **Google Gemini** ‚Üí generates ideas & drafts  \n- **Gmail** ‚Üí email-based approval workflow  \n- **Google Sheets** ‚Üí tracks ideas, drafts, and published posts  \n- **LinkedIn API** ‚Üí posts directly to your company or personal account  \n\n---\n\n## ‚ú® Highlights  \n- üì¨ Email-based approval ‚Üí no dashboards, just reply with a number  \n- üìù 10 AI-generated content ideas + 3 full drafts per topic  \n- üîÑ End-to-end tracking in Google Sheets (`ideas ‚Üí drafts ‚Üí published`)  \n- ‚ö° Auto-posting directly to LinkedIn  \n- ‚úÖ Final confirmation email with preview  \n\n---\n\n## üë§ Best For  \n- Startup founders  \n- Agencies managing multiple clients‚Äô LinkedIn  \n- Solopreneurs & creators who want consistent posting  \n\n---\n\n## üõ†Ô∏è Workflow Overview  \n\n```mermaid\nflowchart TD\n    A[Manual Trigger] --&gt; B[AI Agent - Generate 10 Ideas]\n    B --&gt; C[Code - Parse JSON + Correlation ID]\n    C --&gt; D[Google Sheets - Append Ideas]\n    D --&gt; E[Gmail - Send Ideas Email]\n    E --&gt; F[Gmail Trigger - Await Reply]\n    F --&gt; G[Code1 - Extract Reply Number]\n    G --&gt; H[Google Sheets - Fetch Row]\n    H --&gt; I{Switch Stage}\n    I --&gt;|Ideas| J[AI Agent - Generate 3 Drafts]\n    J --&gt; K[Code3 - Parse Drafts]\n    K --&gt; L[Google Sheets - Update Drafts]\n    L --&gt; M[Gmail - Send Drafts Email]\n    I --&gt;|Drafts| N[Code4 - Select Final Draft]\n    N --&gt; O[LinkedIn - Publish Post]\n    O --&gt; P[Google Sheets - Update Posted]\n    P --&gt; Q[Gmail - Send Confirmation]\n"
